    <h1>Orphan Page</h1>
    <p class="description">A live webpage with <strong>no internal links pointing to it</strong> from anywhere else on the site. Crawlers miss it, link equity never reaches it, and it almost never ranks — despite potentially containing good content.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
