            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>A Botify study found that 26% of pages on large websites are orphan pages — content that exists but receives no internal link equity and is rarely crawled efficiently. For most sites, fixing orphan pages is one of the highest-ROI technical SEO activities available.</p></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>

